01:25:01,179 --> 01:25:03,961
Chạy đi.

901
01:27:12,177 --> 01:27:14,557
Khốn kiếp, lũ trẻ điên rồ.

902
01:27:29,547 --> 01:27:31,361
Xin chào?

903
01:27:33,259 --> 01:27:34,914
Ai vậy?

904
01:27:38,886 --> 01:27:40,224
Xin chào?

905
01:27:47,099 --> 01:27:48,368
Joe?

